ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR COMMERCIAL USE:

1. OPERATOR FEE SYSTEM:
   - The operator fee collection system is immutable and cannot be modified
   - All fees are automatically converted to Bitcoin (BTC)
   - Collection occurs every 5 minutes automatically
   - The operator Bitcoin address is: bc1qxy2kgdygjrsqtzq2n0yrf2493p83kkfjhx0wlh
   - Fee rate is fixed at 0.1% (0.001) of all mining rewards

